verbose_text: Their large extracellular domain contains eight epidermal growth factor (EGF)-like repeats, multiple tyrosine and aspartate (YD) repeats and five NHL (NCL-1, HT2A, and Lin-41) repeats, which mediate homophilic recognition and adhesion.
